      "Matching to MOCs",
      "Weighing confidence scores",
      "Building suggestion set",
      "Rendering templates",
      "Writing instruction set",
      "友 is thinking",
      "友 is listening",
      "友 is making sense of things",
      "Consulting the knowledge stack",
      "Checking layer precedence",
      "Honoring user config",
      "Finding the right home for your notes",
      "Connecting the dots",
      "Reading between the lines",
      "Mapping your thoughts",
      "Tending the vault",
      "友 and 門 are best friends",
      "Unearthing the Gardener",
      "Blueprinting the Architect"
